00|RIO]]<br>{{small|8}} \n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Emerson Indy 250|GAT]]<br>{{small|8}} \n|style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Milwaukee Mile|MIL]]<br>{{small|5}} \n|style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Detroit Indy Grand Prix|DET]]<br>{{small|11}} \n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Portland|POR]]<br>{{small|6}} \n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Cleveland|CLE]]<br>{{small|8}} \n|style=\"background:#DFFFDF;\"| [[Molson Grand Prix of Toronto|TOR]]<br>{{small|4}}  \n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Michigan 500|MCH]]<br>{{small|7}} \n|style=\"background:#FFDF9F;\"| [[Honda 200|MDO]]<br>{{small|3}} \n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| [[Champcar Grand Prix of Road America|ROA]]<br>{{small|8}} \n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Molson Indy Vancouver|VAN]]<br>{{small|25}} \n|style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[Mazda Raceway Laguna Seca#Champ Car|LAG]]<br>{{small|16}} \n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[Grand Prix of Houston|HOU]]<br>{{small|23}} \n|style=\"background:#EFCFFF;\"| [[1998 Honda Indy 300|SRF]]<br>{{small|25}} \n|style=\"background:#CFCFFF;\"| [[1998 Marlboro 500 Presented by Toyota|FON]]<br>{{small|11}} \n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| '''10th'''\n|style=\"background:#CFEAFF;\"| '''82'''\n|}\n\n====Indianapolis 500 results====\n[[File:Bobbyrahal1986.jpg|right|thumb|300px|Rahal during the [[1986 Indianapolis 500|1986 Indy 500]]]]\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Chassis\n! Engine\n! Start\n! Finish\n! Team\n|-\n| [[1982 Indianapolis 500|1982]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n| 17th\n| 11th\n| [[Truesports]]\n|-\n| [[1983 Indianapolis 500|1983]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n| 6th\n| 20th\n| [[Truesports]]\n|-\n| [[1984 Indianapolis 500|1984]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n| 18th\n| 7th\n| [[Truesports]]\n|-\n| [[1985 Indianapolis 500|1985]]\n| [[March Engineering|March]]\n| [[Cosworth]]\n| 3rd\n| 27th\n| [[Truesports]]\n|-\n| [[1986 Indianapolis 5